# Change Log
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
 
The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](http://keepachangelog.com/)
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/).

## [0.0.5] - 2019-12-23

### Changed

- Update serializers.py file to remove duplicate code.
- Update views.py file to provide support for the OPTIONS verb in our RESTful Web Service

## [0.0.4] - 2019-11-28

### Added

- Add toys/urls.py file where we define the urlpatterns list makes it possible to route URLs to views.

### Changed

- Update urls.py file. This file defines the root URL configurations and therefore we must include the URL patterns declared in the previously coded toys/urls.py file
- Minor changes in models.py, and views.py file related with PEP8.

## [0.0.3] - 2019-11-11

### Added

- Add toys/serializers.py file required to manage serialization to JSON and deserialization from JSON.
- Add the toys/migrations/0001_initial.py file. This file includes the code to create the Toy model.

### Changed

- Update .gitignore file.
- Update toys/models.py file to adapt the code to PEP8 guidelines.

## [0.0.2] - 2019-11-07

### Added

- Add Django REST framework and the toys application to the INSTALLED_APPS strings list.

### Changed

- Update README.md file.


## [0.0.1] - 2019-11-06

### Added

- Initial folders and files to begin to build a Django Restful Web Service project called "djrestful".
